{"about_the_game":"BlightFog is a short, narrative driven RPG, where you travel across a post apocalyptic world on a bike while taking care of an infant.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3230290/extras/divider_02.png?t=1729616965\" /><br><br>On the way you will meet other anthropomorphic characters. Solve conflicts and build relationships through dialogues. <br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3230290/extras/05.gif?t=1729616965\" /><br><br>Allocate resources between you and the child, find unique items that will influence dialogues and give you new ways to approach different situations.<br><br>Your goal is to save the child's mother and get them both to safety.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3230290/extras/07.gif?t=1729616965\" /><br><br>Will you chose the longer and safer paths, or risk to save time and fuel and take the shorter but more dangerous ones?<br><br>Will you let the child starve or sacrifice your own well-being for him? Will you be a pretend-hero, a coward or a fuel-drinking madman who refuses to wear clothes?<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3230290/extras/06.gif?t=1729616965\" /><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3230290/extras/divider_01.png?t=1729616965\" /><br><br>Features:<br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Story heavy RPG where you can: drink fuel, run around naked and destroy the world (maybe)<br></li><li>Game remembers your choices<br></li><li>Choose the safe or fast paths<br></li><li>Meet different antropomorphic characters and build relationships with them<br></li><li>Light resource management<br></li><li>Multiple endings</li></ul>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Freedom?","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steams